1. Check out code
2. Config base path at system/application/config/config.php and .htaccess
3. Config db at system/application/config/database.php
4. sudo chown www-data:www-data useravatars system/cache (or chmod 777 if you cannot sudo)
5. Create database and tables

In Production Site:
1. Remove $route['scaffolding_trigger'] = "tmd"; in system/application/config/routes.php (change it to empty string)
2. Change error_reporting(E_ALL) to error_reporting(E_ERROR) in ./index.php